list.abstract: n.真空；真空吸尘器；空白 adj.产生（利用）真空的 v.用吸尘器打扫
《Vacuum Ball》是一款由Nannings Games制作并发行的休闲类动作游戏，于2022年2月24日发售。

yingyinNormal.en: He's working on a paper about nano vacuum tubes, and wants to know if I'd take a look at it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他在写一篇关于纳米真空管的论文，想让我帮他看看。

yingyinNormal.en: Lady, this is my city, I'll find your friend. Alright, party is over. Miron, vacuum.
yingyinNormal.zh: 小姐，这是我的城市，我会找到你的朋友的。好了，聚会结束。迈伦，上吸尘器。

yingyinNormal.en: It's gone all dark and the music is broken. And my vacuum won't work. And my computer has switched off.
yingyinNormal.zh: 屋子里突然黑了，音乐也停止播放了。我的吸尘器也不工作了。还有我的电脑也突然关了。

yingyinNormal.en: But I am ready to be helpful. In fact, I'm gonna go vacuum. Actually I just did that this morning. Okay.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但我已经准备帮忙了。其实，我现在就去吸地板。我今早才吸过一遍。好吧。

yingyinNormal.en: The light has woken baby Alexander. That's all right. I've got the vacuum cleaner. I've got the trumpet.
yingyinNormal.zh: 灯光把宝宝亚历山大吵醒了。没有关系，我们可以用吸尘器来哄她。我们还有小号呢。

yingyinNormal.en: No, no. Don't. Don't. But can you vacuum out the dryer vent before I get home? I will absolutely do that. Thanks.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不，不，不要洗，但你能在我回家前把通风管道清理干净吗？我一定会清理的。谢了。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, if that's the case, Penny will have to get satellite TV and maybe once a week run a vacuum through this place.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那样的话，佩妮得装卫星电视，而且每周吸一吸灰尘。

yingyinNormal.en: Mummy, daddy, it's gone all dark and the music is broken. And my vacuum won't work. And my computer has switched off.
yingyinNormal.zh: 妈妈，爸爸，全变黑了，音乐也停了。我的吸尘器也不管用了。我的电脑也关了。

yingyinNormal.en: Mummy, daddy, it's gone all dark and the music is broken. And my vacuum won't work. And my computer has switched off.
yingyinNormal.zh: 妈妈，爸爸。屋子里突然黑了音乐也停止播放了。我的吸尘器也不工作了。还有我的电脑也突然关了。

yingyinNormal.en: Everyone is tucked up in their beds. Asleep. Baby Alexander is awake. Peppa and George are awake. What's that noise? It's the vacuum cleaner.
yingyinNormal.zh: 大家都上床睡着了。宝宝亚历山大醒了！佩奇和乔治也醒了。那到底是什么声音啊？那是吸尘器的声音。

yingyinNormal.en: Look. I cleaned. I did the windows, I did the floors. I even used all the attachments on the vacuum, except that little round one with the bristles, I don't know what that's for.
yingyinNormal.zh: 瞧，我大扫除了，我擦窗户，拖地板，我用了吸尘器上的所有功能除了那个圆形的之外，它有什么用处？

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

examination_example.sentence: Researchers can study the garbage left on the moon to see how its materials weathered the radiation and <highlight>vacuum</highlight> of space overtime.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 研究人员可以研究留在月球上的垃圾，看看它的材料是如何经受住太空辐射和真空考验的。

examination_example.sentence: Study the effect of radiation and <highlight>vacuum</highlight> on its materials.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 研究辐射和真空对其材料的影响。

examination_example.sentence: The cordless, such as <highlight>vacuum</highlight> cleaners, flashlights, drills and saws came from the technology of these early space programs.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 像真空吸尘器、手电筒、电钻和电锯这样的无绳设备就来自于这些早期太空计划的技术。
